column6: Plup is playing Pikachu with the PT hat. He is fighting an aegis player on small battle field. Plup is currently losing in percent but both have 2 stocks
Plup missed an up air|| and a pyra down air sends him to the top blast zone
Plup is hit by pyra up air for a kill screen|| but survives
Plup takes a down air again|| sending him off the left side blast zone. The Aegis has 2 stocks left at the end of the game
Plup rematches the Aegis|| and they accept
The stage is Final Destination. Plup is tanking tons of damage without landing a single hit
Plup is sent off the top my pyra down air|| without even damaging the aegis
Plup dies to pyra up B|| one stock left
Plup finally takes a stock off aegis
Plup gets the edgeguard with the Tjolt|| the stock count is 1 to 1
Plup nair loops aegis for 34%|| but messed up and gets hit by Pyra Up B
Plup whiffs a dash attack and dies to pyra ftilt|| losing the game
